  <brief_title>Effects of a Whole Body Vibration Training in Patients After Lung Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of a Whole Body Vibration Training on the Exercise Performance in Patients After Lung Transplantation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
